author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at Sora 2, one model that belongs to a set of AIs that just keep evolving. Watching a video used to be solid evidence, now it's gotten to the point where even the biggest skeptics are able to be fooled and sadly that progress doesn't seem to be stopping. Be careful on what you believe. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: We Can't Trust The Internet After Today...
